title: My First Real Entry!
content:
I woke up late cause I'd gone to bed as late as I could last night and still being 30 minutes late for work, I still woke up like shit.
Givsn it was just Saturday then it was usually way calmer than weekdays, I had 2 customers to help and an errand to run assigned to me by my boss.

In the remaining of the time I was "working", I decided to make some improvements to my Rest API in Golang, which is the exact one I'm using now to store this Diary Entry I'm writing on this app.

Work shift was over and I had to decide what I'd do, go to my aunt's because I hadn't been for so long and then go to her friend's baby shower or none of that and proceed to go to my girlfriend's. I missed her and going to someone else's baby shower seemed out of place for me, so I ended up deciding to go sleep with my girl.

Before going, I spent some alone time studying more Flutter to make theme improvements to my app (yes, this one).
